====== inet-4.x ======

2024-10-29  ------ inet-4.5.4 released ------

2024-05-08  Levente Meszaros

	visualizer: Replaced @enum("light", "dark") with documentation.

	Omnetpp now checks the value against the values found in @enum, and these
	parameters allow for arbitrary color names, so the enumeration was wrong.

2023-08-29  ------ inet-4.5.2 released ------

2023-08-24  ------ inet-4.5.1 released ------

2023-04-04  ------ inet-4.5.0 released ------

2023-03-10  Levente Mészáros

	Removed name != nullptr checks from handleParameterChange.

2023-02-21  Zoltan Bojthe

	Fixed issue 819: InterfaceTableVisualizer does not show IPv6 addesses

2022-11-30  Gyorgy Szaszko

	Fix: don't iterate interfaces if there aren't any.

2022-09-26  Andras Varga

	Eliminated static buffer from resolveDirective() by changing return type to std::string.

2022-07-30  Gyorgy Szaszko

	Added directive to PacketDropVisualizer to display drop reason string.

2022-05-13  ------ inet-4.4.0 released ------

2022-03-21  Levente Mészáros

	InterfaceTableVisualizerBase: Changed default format to avoid useless / in network addresses.
	InterfaceTableVisualizerBase: Fixed #710.

2022-03-02  Gyorgy Szaszko

	Added label format string to GateScheduleVisualizer.

2022-03-02  Levente Mészáros

	Renamed Gate*Visualier to GateSchedule*Visualizer.

2021-11-08  Levente Mészáros

	Added @mutable property to parameters which can be changed during the simulation.

2021-11-15  Rudolf Hornig

	Added @mutable property for OMNeT++ 6 compatibility.

2021-09-29  Zoltan Bojthe

	Reduced code variants based on OMNETPP_BUILDNUM.

2021-07-01  Zoltan Bojthe

	Fixed type differences between MSG and c++ code.

2021-05-19  Levente Mészáros

	Added support for the visualization of redundant unicast and multicast stream configurations.

	Supports the visualization of the configuration computed by the TsnConfigurator
	and StreamRedundancyConfigurator.

2021-04-26  Zoltan Bojthe

	Added/updated Enter_Method() info to the signalname in receiveSignal().

2021-04-12  Zoltan Bojthe

	cVisitor::visit() return type changed from void to bool.

2021-03-19  Zoltan Bojthe

	Changed if-else-if ladders in initialize() to separate if statements because
	different stages may have the same number.

2021-02-16  Levente Mészáros

	Added Gate*Visualizer modules that visualize gate scheduling as annotation on network nodes.

2021-01-11  ------ inet-4.3.0 released ------

2020-12-08  Zoltan Bojthe

	Added signalAnimationTimeMode parameter to MediumVisualizerBase.

2020-12-08  Levente Mészáros

	Added extra conditions to support the visualization of noise source transmissions.

2020-12-04  Levente Mészáros

	Moved canvas and OSG visualizers into separate folders.

2020-11-26  Levente Mészáros

	Fixed double delete crashed caused by explicit deletes and deletes due to reference counting.
	Replaced plain pointers with reference counted pointers to osg nodes.
	Extracted common parts into base class between canvas and OSG mobility visualizers.

2020-11-25  Levente Mészáros

	Fixed stale canvas visualization for deleted mobility module, see #555.

2020-11-04  Levente Mészáros

	Changed all visualizer base class destructors into preDelete methods.

2020-10-21  Levente Mészáros

	Moved visualization removal in destructors to visualizer base classes.

2020-07-22  Levente Mészáros

	Renamed InterfaceEntry -> NetworkInterface and interfaceEntry -> networkInterface.

2020-05-18  Levente Mészáros

	Refactored path visualizer base classes to support upcoming packet flow visualization.
	Disabled fading of path visualizations if fadeOutTime is 0 or negative.
	Added statistics such as numPackets and totalLength to path visualization.
	Added explicit parameter to control the subscribed signals in path visualizers.
	Extended path visualization support with labels allowing multiple paths along the same path.
	Renamed mapChunkIds to mapChunks and added chunk parameter.

2020-05-14  Levente Mészáros

	Fixed statistic visualization when multiple statistics are display from the same signal.

2020-03-18  Levente Mészáros

	Added powerDensityMapPixelMode and spectrogramPixelMode parameters.

